---
title: Pan-Fried Gnocchi Pomodoro with Walnut Chive Pesto
description: Gnocchi with pesto is an all time favourite and we’ve given this one a fresh twist, by pan-frying the gnocchi to give it a beautiful crisp texture. We’ve also mixed up the pesto by replacing the usual basil and pine nuts
with chives and walnuts. This dish went down a treat at the HelloFresh Farm, we hope your family loves it too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-gnocchi-pomodoro-wk45-fdd78f61.jpg
